import React from 'react'; function TestResultsDashboard({ summary = {} }) { const { total = 0, passed = 0, failed = 0, duration = '—', languageBreakdown = [] } = summary; const passRate = total > 0 ? ((passed / total) * 100).toFixed(2) : '0.00'; return (
{/* Test Summary */}

📊 Test Summary

✅ Total Tests Run: {total}
🟢 Passed: {passed}
🔴 Failed: {failed}
📈 Pass Rate: {passRate}%
⏱️ Execution Time: {duration}
{/* Language Breakdown */}

🧪 Test Breakdown by Language

{languageBreakdown.length > 0 ? (
    {languageBreakdown.map((lang, idx) => (
  • {lang.name} {lang.total} tests – {lang.passRate}% pass
    • ))}
) : (

No language data available.

)}
); } export default TestResultsDashboard;
